reviewText: My daughter and her grandmother love Peter Rabbit watch at least once a day

Bought this for when the kids visit.  Great life lessons.

DVD includes the following:
Christmas Tale
The Tale of Nutkin on the Run
The Tale of the Wriggley Worms
The Tale of Jemima's Eggs
The Tale of the Great Breakout
The Tale of the Lucky Four Leaf Clover
The Tale of the Unguarded Garden

Having no annoying previews to skip through was the first great thing I noticed. There are enough episodes on this DVD to keep my 3 year old enthralled for a long time. This new show is so adorable - I like to watch it too. That's a rarity in children's shows.
I love Peter Rabbit! He is the very, very best. Can you name the 6 other episodes in the Christmas DVD?
Very good for my great granddaughter.
All 5 of my Grandkids enjoy this series.

I'm not sure if I love or regret buying this. It's been on repeat since opening the package. :)

Such a cute movie with engaging adventures sure to capture the attention of any little munchkin. Great family fun! I would recommend to anyone and everyone 365 days of the year.
my kids love Peter Rabbit - want more videos available
The disc was not damaged, and delivery was prompt. If you're a Pter Rabbit fan like I am, its a must have.
